  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Bing ads designed to encourage people to adopt healthier practices (e.g., stop smoking,
      become physically active, stop consuming harmful content) are shown using the advertising
      system, to test which ads are more effective as apparent in the subsequent queries to Bing
      submitted by users who saw the ads.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
